      <title>共和党参议员说，特朗普要提取斯特凡尼克的联合国提名。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/trump-to-pull-stefanik-s-un-nomination-gop-senator-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱达荷州的共和党参议员吉姆·里施（Jim Risch）表示，白宫打算撤回代表Elise Stefanik作为美国大使的提名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/trump-to-pull-stefanik-s-un-nomination-gop-senator-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 18:03:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥说，美国已经取了至少300张签证，捍卫了驱逐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/rubio-says-us-may-have-pulled-over-300-visas-defends-expulsions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿马可·卢比奥（Marco Rubio）为特朗普政府驱逐了抗议以色列的外国公民的努力，称美国可能已经撤销了300多张签证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/rubio-says-us-may-have-pulled-over-300-visas-defends-expulsions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 17:21:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大保守派的避税计划是多伦多股票的潜在福音</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/canada-conservatives-tax-shelter-plan-is-potential-boon-for-toronto-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大保守党的选举承诺将允许个人避免对国内公司的某些投资所得税受到称赞，这在多伦多的金融区受到称赞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/canada-conservatives-tax-shelter-plan-is-potential-boon-for-toronto-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 17:17:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由民主党FTC委员起诉的特朗普因其解雇而起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/trump-sued-by-democratic-ftc-commissioners-over-their-firings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统提出的美国联邦贸易委员会的两名民主党成员提起诉讼，对一个90年历史的最高法院案件提出了挑战，该案件限制了白宫对独立机构的权力，包括美联储。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/trump-sued-by-democratic-ftc-commissioners-over-their-firings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 16:52:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其驱逐了BBC的记者，他们涵盖了伊斯坦布尔市长抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/turkey-deports-bbc-reporter-who-covered-istanbul-mayor-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其驱逐了一名英国广播公司的记者，这是当局在伊斯坦布尔市长埃克雷姆·伊玛莫格鲁（Ekrem Imamoglu）监禁后，当局对媒体和抗议者的镇定镇定的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/turkey-deports-bbc-reporter-who-covered-istanbul-mayor-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 16:43:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉洪水流向中国，随着美国的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/flood-of-venezuelan-oil-flows-to-china-as-us-raises-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着特朗普政府部署制裁和次要关税来挤压拉丁美洲国家，委内瑞拉正在将对中国的石油出口提高到近两年来最高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/flood-of-venezuelan-oil-flows-to-china-as-us-raises-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 16:33:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>邦迪建议没有信号查询，因为参议员要求调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/senators-seek-formal-review-of-signal-group-chat-episode</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总检察长帕姆·邦迪（Pam Bondi）建议她不会对特朗普政府官员讨论敏感攻击计划的信号小组聊天进行调查，并说人们应该专注于希拉里·克林顿（Hillary Clinton）和乔·拜登（Joe Biden）的失误，这已经是重大调查的主题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/senators-seek-formal-review-of-signal-group-chat-episode</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 14:37:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择SEC面临急剧兴趣的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/trump-s-pick-for-sec-faces-sharp-conflict-of-interest-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保罗·阿特金斯（Paul Atkins）是唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统领导证券交易委员会（Securities and Exchange Commission）的选秀权，面临着与华尔街和数字资产公司的紧密联系的早期政治考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/trump-s-pick-for-sec-faces-sharp-conflict-of-interest-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 14:30:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲领导人拒绝俄罗斯对制裁救济的要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/european-leaders-reject-russian-demands-for-sanctions-relief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲领导人的联盟排除了对俄罗斯进行制裁的可能性，弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）总统要求同意与乌克兰的部分停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/european-leaders-reject-russian-demands-for-sanctions-relief</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 13:55:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
