      <title>波斯尼亚法院寻求国际逮捕塞族领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/bosnia-court-issues-international-arrest-warrant-for-serb-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波斯尼亚 - 黑塞哥维那最高法院针对该国塞族领导人发出了国际逮捕通知，与有争议的数字升级了冲突，他威胁要脱离巴尔干国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/bosnia-court-issues-international-arrest-warrant-for-serb-leader</guid>
